# Best Practices

* Use `map()` when every element needs to be transformed.
* Use `filter()` when selecting elements based on a condition.
* Use `reduce()` when reducing a sequence to a single value.
* Prefer readable code over overly complex nested expressions.
* Import `reduce()` from the `functools` module before using it.

